Cyberpunk style: A futuristic neon-lit control panel with holographic input fields floating in mid-air, some glowing green indicating valid entries and others pulsing angry red with warning symbols. A pair of hands hovers over the interface, one organic human hand and one sleek robotic hand, both reaching toward a flickering data field. The scene is bathed in electric blue and magenta light, with digital particles streaming through the air. In the background, towering data structures rise like skyscrapers in a digital cityscape, their surfaces covered in flowing validation patterns. Rain-slicked surfaces reflect the chaotic glow of error states and successful inputs competing for attention.
